|   rvAgent Skill (YAML)     |     |   Codex Task Definition    |
|                            |     |                            |
|  name: "deploy-service"   | --> |  name: "deploy-service"    |
|  triggers:                 |     |  input: "{service} {env}"  |
|    - pattern: "/deploy"    |     |  instructions: "..."       |
